# Test Requests para Contact API

## Health Check
GET https://localhost:53903/health

###

## Contact Form - Spanish
POST https://localhost:53903/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "María González",
  "email": "jhorsg@gmail.com",
  "subject": "Consulta sobre servicios de traducción",
  "message": "Hola, me gustaría obtener más información sobre sus servicios de traducción legal. Tengo varios documentos que necesito traducir del español al inglés para un proceso de inmigración.",
  "language": "es"
}

###

## Contact Form - English
POST https://localhost:53903/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Smith",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "subject": "Translation services inquiry",
  "message": "Hello, I would like to get more information about your commercial translation services. I need to translate marketing materials from English to Spanish for our Latin American market.",
  "language": "en"
}

###

## Contact Form - French
POST https://localhost:53903/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pierre Dubois",
  "email": "pierre@example.com",
  "subject": "Demande de traduction technique",
